 <name>sfDB4toPropelPlugin</name>
 <channel>pear.symfony-project.com</channel>
 <summary>The sfDB4toPropelPlugin allows to transform a DB4 schema into a valid Propel schema.yml file</summary>
 <description>sDB4toPropelPlugin is a plugin that adds to symfony a new task: propel:db4-to-propel that allows you to convert a DB4 schema (a DBDesigner4 schema) into a valid Propel schema.yml file, with this plugin you can just forget the boring work of building your schema.yml by hand. ;)</description>
